The burgers taste homemade. The fixins are free. The strawberry milkshake is frothy! They don't just have burgers, they also have tasty fries. Discovered this place on GrubHub and order numerous times. Decided to stop by. They have daily specials for $7, that's a chicken, turkey, beef burger or salmon burger depending on the day w fries and lemonade. They have 2 for $5 chicken or turkey burgers every day. The kids meal is $7 too. They have wraps, different kinds of Mac and salads too. Veggie menu. Best to order ahead but the wait isn't too long. If that's not enough, u can have it your way like that other fast food song but feel better about what u are putting in your body for a little bit more.
